{"tid":331731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 學 日 文 靠 睇 愛 情 動 作 片","createTime":"2017-07-22T12:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T10:46:52.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f59e98607a66cd165c72861d6cd78f7fd917793a","tid":331731,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤昨日到電台宣傳新歌《傷心到變形》，講到早前到沖繩拍MV，問到有沒有艷遇，他說：「我喺酒吧畀咗100蚊美金同個伯伯飲酒，用僅餘嘅日文同佢溝通。（日文喺邊學返嚟？）日本愛情同動作片囉，最近有學泰拳，希望有機會可以拍到有愛情元素嘅動作片。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，講到美國搖滾樂隊Linkin Park主音Chester Bennington疑因抑鬱症自殺身亡，問到坤坤如何應對負面情緒？他說：「我通常自閉一排，沉澱一下就會重生，覺得自己嘅抗壓性都唔錯，我係打不死嘅吳業坤！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20170722/photo/0722-00282-042b1.jpg?t=1500724545649\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170722%2Fphoto%2F0722-00282-042b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1500724545649&h=795d185a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3986b565fb4e3899047461036e6cc0b814e4c515","tid":331731,"uid":106858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:12:49.000Z","msg":"無人想知呀"},{"pid":"61f203a2169cf4adb1ec2ca38790a00273476ed8","tid":331731,"uid":74012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"條撚樣係咪在酒吧同鬼佬講 &quot;熱菇&quot;/ &quot;気持ち&quot;?<br />\n<br />\nhehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8162d5bdeceddbbb68a98cb8d2d5ef916e309a","tid":331731,"uid":36366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fk653g7n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffk653g7n&h=b10421c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"326263cf32ed7b84659f146f820a034b9039569c","tid":331731,"uid":34498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170514/photo/bkn-20170514162607726-0514_00862_001_03b.